                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">User input: DecimalNonnegative;  Note: Either R-value or U-factor is required, not both. The same descriptor (R-value or U-factor) should be used throughout this table. If user enters R-value, it is stored in InsulationExteriorRValue; Else If user enters U-factor it is stored in InsulationExteriorUFactor</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
